<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>도움말 - 마법연구회</title>

        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/base.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/badges.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/buttons.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/cards.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/user/mypage.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <script>
            (function() {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme);
            })();
        </script>
        <div id="root">
            <%- include('../partials/header') %>

            <main class="main-content">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="mypage-header">
                        <h1 class="title">도움말</h1>
                    </div>

                    <div class="help-section">
                        <div class="help-category">
                            <h3>시작하기</h3>
                            <div class="help-items">
                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">account_circle</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>회원가입 및 로그인</h4>
                                        <p>마법연구회에 가입하여 다양한 서비스를 이용해보세요. 이메일 인증을 통해 안전하게 계정을 생성할 수 있습니다.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">person</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>프로필 설정</h4>
                                        <p>마이페이지에서 프로필 사진, 닉네임, 소개글을 설정할 수 있습니다.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="help-category">
                            <h3>주요 기능</h3>
                            <div class="help-items">
                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">library_books</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>아카이브</h4>
                                        <p>다양한 소설과 작품들을 탐색하고 읽어보세요.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">groups</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>커뮤니티</h4>
                                        <p>다른 회원들과 소통하고 의견을 나누세요. 게시글 작성, 댓글, 좋아요 기능을 통해 활발한 소통이 가능합니다.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">sentiment_satisfied</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>마연회콘</h4>
                                        <p>마법연구회만의 특별한 이모지 시스템입니다. 다양한 감정과 상황을 표현할 수 있는 커스텀 이모지를 사용해보세요.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">science</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>마법연구소</h4>
                                        <p>마법연구소입니다.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="help-category">
                            <h3>문제 해결</h3>
                            <div class="help-items">
                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">bug_report</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>버그 신고</h4>
                                        <p>서비스 이용 중 문제가 발생했나요? <a href="/feedback">피드백 및 버그 신고</a> 페이지를 통해 문제를 신고해주세요.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-item">
                                    <div class="help-icon">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">contact_support</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="help-content">
                                        <h4>직접 문의</h4>
                                        <p>궁금한 점이나 건의사항이 있으시면 <a href="/contact">문의하기</a> 페이지를 통해 연락해주세요.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

        <style>
            .help-section {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 2.5rem;
            }

            .help-category h3 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
                padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
            }

            .help-items {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.5rem;
            }

            .help-item {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                background: var(--card-background);
                border-radius: 1rem;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow);
                transition: all 0.2s ease;
            }

            .help-item:hover {
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .help-item:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            }

            [data-theme='dark'] .help-icon {
                background: #8b5cf6;
            }

            .help-icon {
                flex-shrink: 0;
                width: 48px;
                height: 48px;
                background: var(--primary-color);
                border-radius: 0.75rem;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                color: white;
            }

            .help-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .help-content h4 {
                color: var(--text-primary);
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            }

            .help-content p {
                color: var(--text-secondary);
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin: 0;
            }

            .help-content a {
                color: var(--primary-color);
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .help-content a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .help-item {
                    padding: 1rem;
                }

                .help-icon {
                    width: 40px;
                    height: 40px;
                }

                .help-icon .material-symbols-outlined {
                    font-size: 1.25rem;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </body>
</html> 